{"tid":1062183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(15/3) 元朗16歲仔成功重刷首抽！","createTime":"2019-03-15T02:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T09:09:26.000Z","uid":202464,"like":22,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":40,"remark":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：\n[url]https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline[/url]","replies":[{"pid":"fc89f1a6bf2714ff73c7d4caa49078f3a47b2df0","tid":1062183,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"一名16歲青年清晨近6時，在元朗朗屏邨高處墮下，倒臥畫屏樓對開，波鞋飛脫，爆頭當場死亡。警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n警員清晨5時57分接報到場調查，於現場未有檢獲遺書，初步相信青年從一梯間墮下，事件沒有可疑，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190315/_2019031509082535052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190315%2F_2019031509082535052.jpg&h=c5497823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1456257/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1456257%2F&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsac%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=7403da15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1456257%2F&h=c4a617d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1456257/</a>"},{"pid":"6f437d7feafe122a54c4f8c703589316b829fb41","tid":1062183,"uid":202464,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:26:38.000Z","msg":"(14/3）薄扶林私樓17歲仔，成功重刷首抽！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190314/large/1552569864_6940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190314%2Flarge%2F1552569864_6940.jpg&h=09feab20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n薄扶林置富花園富榮苑一單位，晚上8時許，一名穿着校服的17歲青年於寓所內上吊，其家人發現報案。青年事後由救護車送往瑪麗醫院搶救，惜終告不治。警方正調查青年上吊原因。"},{"pid":"32e3e908fcbdd391d509e26affe9cf5f91e54994","tid":1062183,"uid":2